snippet.textDisplay:
This song samples a Tupac song that samples a Boosty Collins' song.

Eazy-E sampled it in 1991, Beyonce sampled it in 2003, and Childish Gambino sampled it in 2016.
Eamon sampled Eazy-E's version in 2004 (one of my favourites), Malow Mac sampled the Tupac version in 2006, as did Z-Ro in 2009.

A classic song, sampled many times in great ways.
